    <item>
      <title>C ile Nesne Yaratmak</title>
      <link>https://blog.askin.ws/blog/c-ile-nesne-yaratmak/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Apr 2010 04:08:00 +0300</pubDate>
      <author>askin@askin.ws (Aşkın Özgür)</author>
      <guid>https://blog.askin.ws/blog/c-ile-nesne-yaratmak/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.askin.ws/uploads/2010/04/c3po.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; title=&#34;C-3PO&#34;&gt;Evet kışkırtıcı bir başlık attım :)
Aslında yapacağımız olay bir structı nesne gibi kullanmak. Buna benzer bir kodu yıllar önce görmüştüm. O günden bu güne sürekli böyle bir şeyi nasıl yaparım diye araştırdım. Anca bugün çözebildim olayı ;)
Kodu aşağıda yorum satırıyla beraber veriyorum. Yorumlarda gerekli açıklamaları yaptım.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu yazıyla C-3PO nun ne lakası var diyebilirsiniz. C ile resim ararken karşıma bu çıktı, bende boş durmasın dedim :)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-c&#34; data-lang=&#34;c&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;/*
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt; * Sınıfımızı yaratıyoruz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt; */&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; _myobject {
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// alt alanlar
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; a, b;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;/*
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;   * Metod
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;   * Burada fonksiyon pointerı tanımlıyoruz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;   */&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;add)(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; _myobject&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt;);
};

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// struct ön ekinden kurtuluyoruz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;typedef&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;struct&lt;/span&gt; _myobject MyObject;

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;/*
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt; * Asıl işi yapacak fonksiyonu tanımlıyoruz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt; * MyObject structını parametre olarak alıyor
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt; */&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;realAdd&lt;/span&gt;(MyObject&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; a) {
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; a&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;a &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; a&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;b;
}

&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;main&lt;/span&gt; ( &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; ) {
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;/*
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;   * Nesnemizi oluşturuyoruz.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;   * add pointerına fonksiyonu atıyoruz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;   */&lt;/span&gt;
  MyObject mo &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;, realAdd};
  printf(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;A + B = %d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, mo.add(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt;mo));
  &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;;
}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Kodun başına stdio.h headerını eklemekte fayda var. WP sıkıntı çıkarttığı için silmek zorunda kaldım. Kodun düzgün halini &lt;a href=&#34;http://github.com/askin/misc/raw/master/fun/struct-function.c&#34;&gt;burada&lt;/a&gt; bulabilirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
